@using Corsinvest.ProxmoxVE.Admin.Core.Common
@inherits AdminComponentBase

<RadzenAlert AlertStyle="AlertStyle.Warning" AllowClose="false" Text="@L[Messages.WebShellPamUserRequired]" />

<Overview3Cols>
    <Text1>
        <strong>Node Protect</strong> is a powerful tool designed to back up the configuration settings of Proxmox VE nodes, ensuring easy restoration in case of failures or issues.<br />
        By backing up critical node configurations, administrators can quickly restore a node to its previous state, reducing downtime and simplifying recovery.<br />
        This tool is essential for environments where node configurations are complex or critical to system stability.<br />
    </Text1>

    <Text2>
        <strong>Easy Restoration</strong>: Ensures that node configurations can be restored quickly and accurately, minimizing system downtime.<br />
        <strong>Data Security</strong>: Protects against configuration loss, providing peace of mind in case of hardware failure or misconfigurations.<br />
        <strong>Efficient Backup Management</strong>: Automates and manages node configuration backups, ensuring timely and reliable backups.<br />
    </Text2>

    <Text3>
        <strong>Seamless Integration</strong>: Designed for simple integration with Proxmox VE, ensuring minimal setup and efficient backup of configurations.<br />
        <strong>Reliable Recovery</strong>: Provides a reliable solution for restoring critical configurations, ensuring continuity and reducing manual intervention.<br />
        <strong>Enhanced System Stability</strong>: By maintaining backups of node configurations, Node Protect helps ensure that system performance and stability are quickly restored after disruptions.<br />
    </Text3>
</Overview3Cols>
